  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Objectives: Evaluation of the clinical long-term safety, tolerability, patient satisfaction,
      pharmacokinetics and pattern of use of oral prucalopride tablets given in doses up to 4 mg
      once daily to patients with chronic constipation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
